_sText: This is a hosties map created by me, TheLostCause, made for one of my friends at the BlackCrypt Clan. This map has, 2 jails, a shot for shot room, a rebel door, a ct assault hole, a gun toss area,a gun pit, and a secret weapon area. I hope you guys please download it and play it. Also don't forget to rate and critique it so i can learn how to make better hostie maps in the future as this is my first one. Thank you and if you actually read this whole thing then your awesome ;)
